    "content":"<div class='t-c'><p><strong><h2>不忘初心跟党走，咏颂筑梦新时代<h2></strong></p></div><div class='t-c'><p><strong><h2>我校举行学习宣传贯彻党的十九大精神中华经典诵读会<h2></strong></p></div><div class='t-c'><p><strong>中华经典诵读会</strong></p></div><p>新时代绘就新蓝图，新征程开创新局面。为全面学习贯彻党的十九大精神，实验小学党总支迅速响应，多措并举，精心组织做好党的十九大各项学习宣传工作，在全校师生中掀起了学习宣传贯彻十九大精神的热潮。</p><p>12月26日下午，实验小学三楼演播厅座无虚席，教职工学习宣传贯彻党的十九大精神中华经典诵读会拉开了序幕。</p><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-1.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-2.jpg' /></div><p>诵读会分为“大国泱泱”、“砥砺前行”、“继往开来”、“伟大复兴”四个篇章，我校语文教师们用朗诵、吟唱、演奏、舞蹈等方式来呈现经典诗篇的魅力。</p><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-3.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-4.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-5.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-6.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-7.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-8.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-9.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-10.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-11.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-12.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-13.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-14.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-15.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-16.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-17.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-18.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-19.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-20.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-21.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-22.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-23.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-24.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-25.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-26.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-27.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-28.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-29.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-30.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-31.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-32.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-33.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-34.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-35.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-36.jpg' /></div><div class='t-c'><img class='pt' src='publish/journal/sqsy/中华经典诵读会-37.jpg' /></div><p>中华优秀经典文化是涵养社会主义核心价值观的重要源泉，是中国人的精神礼赞，有浸润心灵、启迪人心的力量。本次活动旨在以中华优秀经典作品为纽带，学习宣传贯彻党的十九大精神，大力弘扬中华优秀文化，激励广大师生不忘初心、牢记使命、永远奋斗。</p><p>巍巍中华天下为公，华夏精髓含蕴其中。一心向党扎根讲台，传承经典我心永恒。</p>"
